{"tid":1913822,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"明報：離開加拿大 回支那避難","createTime":"2020-03-07T05:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T06:16:29.000Z","uid":6497,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d9aba0df4ef262b8b8d8b093d30851a063ba4d6c","tid":1913822,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BOTP5Aj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBOTP5Aj.jpg&h=2e4f9d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/346345732128888/posts/2728003390629765/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F346345732128888%2Fposts%2F2728003390629765%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=c0bb38bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/346345732128888/posts/2728003390629765/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n離開加拿大<br />\n回中國避肺炎<br />\n<br />\n加拿大的新冠肺炎疫情現時不很嚴重，但大家覺得會愈來愈嚴重。不斷增加確診病例下，官方不斷說，沒社區爆發，感染機會很低。官方愈講得有信心，大家愈擔心。大家問：加拿大疫情一旦大爆發，怎辦？答案是：回中國暫避。不是因為最危險的地方最安全，而是大家吃「硬」不吃「軟」，想知更多，請留意明天出版的「明報星期6周刊」。"},{"pid":"186f74133aa2732e103c40b79483a9752cf1d01c","tid":1913822,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T05:59:46.000Z","msg":"睇下有幾多人會番？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be367ddea1b36b691c4eae2a1925bdd8070adca","tid":1913822,"uid":124452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"非常支持，支那畜係走就快"},{"pid":"62efb639acfbc7acec63402595a3049b448150fe","tid":1913822,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:16:29.000Z","msg":"滯留在疫情蔓延的國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一個咪就係中國囉屌"}]}